# Contributing to [Project Name]

Thank you for considering contributing to this project! We welcome contributions from developers of all experience levels. This guide will help you get started in under 15 minutes.

## Code of Conduct

Please read and respect our [CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md](CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md). We are committed to providing a welcoming and inclusive environment for all contributors.

